Quickstrike:




The platform of the CR tank accended, revealing the repaired Quickstrike. 
The Fuzor coughed from surprise. He remembered being in the forest, trying 
to escape a granade, but next part he remembered him waking up in CR fluid. 
He paniced a little. His eyes were wide, looking around the area, finding 
himself in familiar surroundings. It was the cave of the Predacon base.

He shook his head and stood up. He looked over and saw Stingtra. He leaped 
over to her.

"What in tarnation happened?" he asked her, looking back at the CR tank.
